quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  103,1,(Passage of) time (through the ages) acts as a witness
  103,2,"Verily, the human being is surely in loss"
  103,3,"except those who have developed Faith and performed righteous deeds, and indulged in mutual teaching with Al-Haqq; and mutually prescribed to one another steadfastness (patience and perseverance)"